        <p>I do not release this data until 10 years after your death. This also applies to data obtained from public sources.</p>

        <h5>Storage period of your personal data</h5>
        <p>Your personal data will not be retained for longer than is strictly necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected. If you have not been active on our website for 3 years, your membership will be terminated and the personal data associated with your account will be deleted. The personal data processed on your personal page for the purpose of my genealogical research will never be deleted. I believe that this data is of historical importance for my genealogical research.</p>

        <p>However, you may request from me that this data may only be viewed by the researcher himself and not by registered close relatives. Your personal page is therefore fully protected for members of this website. Your data is also protected from visitors to this website at all times.</p>

